  "title": "Flavour QC Analyst (6m contract) #HAC",
  "description": "<p><strong>Note: Must have no food allergy / dietary restrictions</strong></p><p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform inspections on raw materials, intermediates and finished products by conduct sensory evaluation, carry out physical, analytical tests to ensure compliance with specifications and standards.</li><li>Perform basic checks, calibration and maintenance of test equipment to ensure that test results are accurate.</li><li>Assist and support in non-conformance and investigations of customers’ complaint samples or rejected items (Internal & External).</li><li>Manage the overall QC status of all final products and perform SAP for final products to facilitate shipment.</li><li>Ensure lab stock is sufficient for lab use</li></ul><p></p><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Food Science or related </li><li>1-3 years of experience in QC </li><li>Able to start immediately </li></ul><p><strong>Interested candidates please send your resume to anna.chen@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong><br /><strong></strong></p><p>Anna Chen jiaxin</p><p>CEI No: R25157621</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd  </p><p>EA License: 99C4599</p>",
